Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}威力战士\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Powertron!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}联合-攻击!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Special Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可恶 下次我不会放过你们的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Curses! I'll get you next time, Powertron!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}BUG之王 别跑\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hold it, Kingburg!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可恶 让他跑了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Dammit! Did he get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过 我们会保护 这网络世界的和平\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}However, we Powertrons will uphold the peace of the network!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}耶!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟电视里的感觉不一样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}That was nothing like the stuff on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看着好俗气\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}That was so cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么这么贵啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Man, that's like way too expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为是广岛演唱会那一场的现场碟\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Like I said, it's from that show in Hiroshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是我没去的那次?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}The one I couldn't go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小丽被那群人闹场捣乱 唱不下去了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}When Rei went fumbling her song 'coz those guys started trouble…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之后未麻顶替小丽接着唱 碟里全录了下来\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}And this is the MiniDisc from when Mima sang in Rei's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻唱小丽的歌 很珍贵哦\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It's a precious sample of Mimarin's singing voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.07,0:01:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 另外 那个传闻是真的吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, yeah… Is that rumor true?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 那个\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只剩三本 只剩三本\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Three left, only three left…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Cham的最新报导 只剩三本\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Last issue of CHAMMINGBIRD… only three left.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}400元 400元\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}400 yen… 400 yen…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也听说了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yeah, I read about that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听说她今天就要宣布 因为这是她在这里的最后一场演唱会了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I heard she's announcing it today coz it's the last concert here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就这么小的一场演唱会? 未麻可有点冷漠哦\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}At a nothing show like this? That's pretty cold of Mimarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最近未麻的单独活动越来越多了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}There's been lots of solo activity going on lately…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她也确实挺适合当演员的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}And only Mimarin's like worthy of being an actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看 那些人又来了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Look, they're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上个礼拜就是他们来捣乱\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}The guys that caused trouble last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望今天不要又来乱搞\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I just hope they don't make a mess today, of all days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好紧张\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm getting nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要动 不要动\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Come on, sit still!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这个是怎么了 缝线都磨掉了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hey, what's up with this!? This is all frayed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦?我不知道啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}-给我一些透明胶带 -喂?你好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}-Get me some masking tape! -Hello? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}记住你第二首歌的前奏 未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Remember your entrance in the second song, Mima!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别给我压力啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Don't pressure me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要喝水\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I need a drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}-对不起 过会儿我给你打回去 -唱完再喝\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}-I'm sorry. I'll call you back. -You can have drinks after the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要上了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}看来她们已经准备好了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}And it looks like they're set.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}有请她们登场 掌声欢迎 CHAM\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Without further adieu, please welcome to our stage… CHAM!!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻 未麻 未麻 未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mima! Mima! Mima!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}未麻应该演戏而不是唱歌\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Mima should be acting, not singing!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}我做不到\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}I can't do this after all!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}莉香…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Mika…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他们想让她演电视剧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}They want her in a drama series.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再好不过了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}There are no better deals than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么不能边唱边演?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}She can act AND sing! That should be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她和组合里的另外两人 日程安排已经有冲突了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Her schedule with the other two is already starting to mismatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她没有受过演员的训练\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}She didn't go through those hard lessons to become an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}电视制作人已经称赞过未麻的演技了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}The TV producer praised Mima's acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是未麻自己的感受呢?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But what about MIMA'S feelings!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢大家\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是一场开心的演唱会 但我们只剩下一首歌了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It was a fun concert, but we only have one song left…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可我们才刚来啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}We just got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 在唱最后一首歌之前 有件事要向大家宣布\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Umm… Before our last song, we have news to tell you…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 在CHAM的这些年 未麻很开心…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Um, I, Mima Kirigoe, had a fun time as a member of CHAM…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一边呆着去\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们干什么了?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What did we do!? HUH!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别装了 臭打工的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Quit showin' off! You're only a part-timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}滚一边去 混蛋\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Outta my face, ya asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}滚出去!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}YOU get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么 你叫谁滚出去 混蛋\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What the hell!? Who are you telling to leave, you fucker!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是我说的…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}刚才扔罐子的人 给我出来\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What are you doing!? Get the hell over here, whoever threw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}滚出去! 滚出去!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Go home! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}-妈的 -滚出去! 滚出去! 滚出去!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}-Dammit! -Go home! Go home! Go home! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又来了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}终止演出吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}We're canceling the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可今天是…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But today is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}闭嘴 妈的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Shut up! Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}滚出去 滚出去 滚出去 滚出去\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Go home! Go home! Go home! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}停下\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Today…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本来希望能和大家 一起开心的度过\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Just today… I wanted to have a good time with all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有些人是什么态度\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What attitude from some no-namer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你这家伙\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You little!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你这怪胎想干嘛\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What do you want, you freak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们走\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其实 今天 我…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}A-Actually… as of today, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从今天起 未麻就要离开CHAM了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}As of today, Mima will graduate from CHAM!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么? 为什么?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}-What!? -Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢大家\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在CHAM的两年半里 我和大家度过了美好的时光\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm really happy that I spent the last 2 1/2 years with you all as part of CHAM!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今后 我会尽力去做好一个演员 也希望大家支持\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I hope you'll support me as I do my best as a rookie actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是我的最后一首歌\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}So this will be my last song. Please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对她的经纪人来说 这么做是理所当然\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Well, it totally makes sense from the agency's point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做偶像歌手确实赚不到钱啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Pop idols just don't make money… right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人得往高处走啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Metamorphosis, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻 别离开我们 别走\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}-Mimarin! -Don't leave us! Don't quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻 未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mimarin! Mimarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一直都在看未麻之部屋\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm always looking at Mima's Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟糕 乳酪坏掉了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Geez! This cheese already went bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真抱歉 昨天忘了喂你们\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm sorry… I forgot to feed you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}今天发生的地震\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}The earthquake that happened in Mie prefecture…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}摧毁了整个地区\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}flattened towns throughout the region.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}政府报告两百人死亡 但是 总受灾人数 尚无法确定\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}The government reports 200 dead, but the total number of victims are…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}很多人被压在瓦砾下 生死未明\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}yet to be determined since many more are missing amid the rubble.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}当局已经派遣军队展开救援\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Authorities have called in troops for rescue operations…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}但由于该地区没有恢复照明…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}however, because the area is already getting dark…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这几年工作辛苦了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Thanks for all the work over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再见了 偶像歌手未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Bye bye, Mima the pop idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}"请永远为我们唱下去"\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"Sing for us forever"…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我真的做不到\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I really can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我喜欢看未麻之部屋 我已经与{\fs15}(未麻的房间){\fs}建立了联系\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"I always like looking into Mima's Room. I've put up a link to Mima's Room."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}-喂 -未麻 你在家啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\b0}-Hello? {\i1}-Mima! You're home!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妈妈\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我很好 你呢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yeah, I'm fine! How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 今天是最后一次 以后我不会再唱歌了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yeah. Today was the last one. No more singing for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}我记得你以前一直想做歌手的啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}I remember when you kept saying you wanted to be a singer.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是我的一个好机会 我已经跟你说过了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}This is my big chance! I told you that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}我们一直很喜欢你的歌\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Lately, we've all been looking forward to each new single!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:12:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}你爷爷每次都要买20张碟\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Your uncle over in Yamaguchi buys 20 copies every time!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不了解这个行业 妈妈\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You just don't understand this industry, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}你不是最会唱歌吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Wasn't singing what you were best at?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偶像歌手的形象限制了我的发展\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}The pop idol image is suffocating me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再说 如今偶像…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Besides, nowadays pop idols are…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下 有电话打进来\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Wait, I've got a call on the other line…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yes, Kirigoe here…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妈 是打错的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mom? Just a wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我知道\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噢 等一下 浴室\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, wait! The bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}五分钟后再打过来\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Call me back in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噢 老妈\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}传真?谁发来的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}A fax? Who's it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(叛徒 叛徒 叛徒 叛徒 叛徒 叛徒)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Traitor traitor traltor TRAiTor TrAltoR TralTor{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"Who are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"Who are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留美 你知道那是什么意思吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Do you know what that note means, Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是个互联网的网址\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It's an Internet home page.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噢 这个最近好像很流行\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, that thing that's been popular lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那究竟是什么呢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}And what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么说呢…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}How can I describe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就相当于是把电脑连在一起\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It's kind of like computer networks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后呢?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}And?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比如这个人说的 "与未麻之部屋 建立了联系"\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Considering that this person "put up a link to Mima's Room"…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那这个"未麻之部屋" 就应该是个网站的名字\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}this "Mima's Room" thing is the title of a web site.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你一点也没听懂吧?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯! 完全不懂!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Nope. Not one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉让大家久等\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们已经准备好了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}We're ready for the take!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别逗我笑\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明是自己要笑\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You're laughing on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}5秒钟\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}5 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}4 3 2\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}4, 3, 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个被谋杀的莉香 她的妹妹来了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}The younger sister of Rika, the murder victim, is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要见她吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Would you like to see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}山城君\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mr. Yamashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你知不知道犯人为什么要剥下受害人的皮\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Do you know why the culprit peels off the skin of his victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想他能从中得到某种性快感?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I assume he gets sexual stimulation from such activities…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:15:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他是想要成为一个… 成为什么?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}-He wants to become one. -Become… what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一个女人 或者…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}A woman… or…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卡!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}CUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}落合小姐果然是个厉害的演员\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Eri Ochiai is a great actress after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}摄影机一开 她就好像变成了另外一个人\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}She's a completely different person when the camera is rolling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下一幕 第32幕\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}NEXT! Scene 32!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}莉香的妹妹 该你了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Rika's sister, you're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}帮我拿着\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hold this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}紧张吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有一点\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}A bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就只有一句台词 也没什么可紧张的啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Not much to get nervous about when you have only one line…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们的大明星怎么样了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}How's our star actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}田所先生 她就要开始了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mr. Tadokoro. She's just going on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"Who are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"Who are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"Who…"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:16:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是这么回事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}That's what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早上好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早上好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早上好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗨 大家好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hello, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早上好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}涉谷老师也来啦\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mr. Shibuya! You're here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早上好 惠利 感觉怎么样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hi, Eri. How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先生 你写的台词好绕口 我实在念不下去了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Sir, your lines are too hard! I don't want to do it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要这么说\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但剧情太完美了 我最喜欢这种类型\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But the story is really good!! I love stuff like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘴真够甜的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You're good at egging people on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}惠利 这是你的影迷来信\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Eri. There were this many fan letters sent to the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多谢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Thank you, Mr. Tejima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小黑\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Kuro…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃 这封不是给你的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, this one's not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好好工作\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Well, keep up the good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老师 告诉我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}So, Sir, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}凶犯到底是谁啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Who's the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 不能说 说了就没意思了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Sorry, can't tell you. That'd spoil the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那你到底准备把凶犯怎么样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}So what ARE you going to do about the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要快点做决定了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You're gonna have to make your mind up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早上好 手岛先生、涉谷老师\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Good morning, Mr. Tejima! Mr. Shibuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噢 你好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, hello there…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻在剧组里的评价不错\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mima's getting good reviews. Even among station staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然这样 她的戏份 好像少了点吧 哈\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}If that's the case, don't you think she's got too few lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听到没? 涉谷\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}So he says, Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 不要看我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hey, don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老师 多给未麻点机会嘛\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Sir! Please! Make use of Mima just a little bit more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是她是个偶像歌手 不是吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But see… She's a pop idol, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这不太好用啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}They're really hard to use…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那没关系 她已经不是偶像歌手了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}That's no problem! She's done with being a pop idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们要给她的形象 来个大转变\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}We want to give her a drastic image change, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们准备好了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}We're ready for the take!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对了 这个给未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, this is for Mima.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"Who are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"Who are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}5秒钟\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}5 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}4 3 2\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}4, 3, 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}田所先生!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mr. Tadokoro!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}田所先生!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mr. Tadokoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}田所先生!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mr. Tadokoro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我没事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是怎么回事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What the hell is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想是那封信爆炸了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I think that letter just exploded!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫救护车 叫救护车\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Call an ambulance! An ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(这是一次警告 下一次 将是动真的)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Is a warning. The next one will be REAL.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}We're all set now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留美 你真棒\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Rumi, you're really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在我帮你登陆上网\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'll sign you up for online services now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留美 你觉得怎么样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What do you think, Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那天的那件事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}About that thing the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 那个\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, that…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信用卡号码\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Credit card number…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要不要叫警察\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Shouldn't we have called the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}田所说不用 我们也没办法\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mr. Tadokoro said not to. We can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可这是犯罪啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But it was a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也许遭殃的本来应该是我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}And it might have been me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没关系 只不过是个恶作剧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It's okay. It was just a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且田所伤得不重\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Fortunately, Mr. Tadokoro wasn't badly hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以未麻你也不用担心\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}So you shouldn't worry, Mima.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻 我把这解释给你听 认真听着\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Anyway, Mima, I'll explain all of this so listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是万维网的浏览器\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}This is a browser for the World Wide Web.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你双击这个就会启动了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You launch it by double-clicking here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}双击是啥?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Wha? Double-clip?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要打断我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What are you going to do with a clip?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看 在地址栏中 键入URL\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}See, next to "location" you enter the URL.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不难吧?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It's not hard, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜托 留美\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Come on, Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你可以用日语跟我解释吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Can't you explain it to me in Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是 你啥都不懂 买个电脑来干嘛\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Boy! Why did you buy a computer when you don't know anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为他们都说很简单\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Because they said it was easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吧 我从头再给你讲一遍\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, all right. I'll explain it from the beginning once more…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}h t t p\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}H… T… T… P…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有东西了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Ooh, something came up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈 我干得挺好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hey, I'm doing pretty well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}And now…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找到了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(未麻之部屋)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Mima's Room{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(未麻之部屋)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Mima's Room{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(未麻的日记)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Mima's Diary{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}这是什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Mima's Diary{\i} What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真糟糕\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"It was just terrible!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我搞砸了舞蹈 忘记了歌词\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"I screwed up the choreography, AND forgot my lyrics."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我对不起我的歌迷\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"I feel so sorry to all my fans!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天早上 我左脚先下了火车\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"This morning, when I got off the train left foot first…"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}结果引来一天的倒霉事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"was when all the bad stuff started."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一直注意上火车或者\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"I always make it a point that my right foot…"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}进浴室时 要先迈右脚\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"goes first into the train and into the bath."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有人真的很了解我 这是什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Someone sure knows me! What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.29,0:21:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天是我21岁生日\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"Today was my 21st birthday."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雪子 小丽和其他同事给我搞了个聚会 好开心\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"Yukiko, Rei, and the staff at the agency held a party for me. It was terrific!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回家前 我去那家超市买了点东西\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"Coming home, I went grocery shopping at the usual store."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我买了矿泉水和牛奶\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"I got mineral water and milk."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}牛奶买的是高档的母牛牌的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"The milk just has to be Cow Brand milk."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偶尔要对自己好一点\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"I have to allow myself at least this much luxury."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:22:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还买了鱼食\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"And food for my precious fish, of course…"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}5月12日 Double Bind剧组里 落合惠利小姐的表演给我印象很深\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"May 12th. I was impressed with Eri Ochiai's performance in Double Bind."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一开拍她就像是变了个人\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"She's another person when the camera is rolling…"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.28,0:22:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这些都是什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.62,0:22:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他们怎么会知道这么多\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}How do they know this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}你是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Who are you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}你是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Who are you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}你是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Who are you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}你是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Who are you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}你是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Who are you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}你是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Who are you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.89,0:22:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是心理医生浅宫瞳子\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm Dr. Toko Asamiya, specializing in psychiatry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是你已过世姐姐的心理医生\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I was your late sister's psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有些问题想问你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}There are some things I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.11,0:22:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}山城警探 又一个\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Detective Yamashiro! Another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.15,0:22:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}这已经是第五个了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}This is the fifth victim…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总共才3个镜头\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Just three shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为这个离开CHAM值得吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Is this work really worth leaving CHAM for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留美 你知不知道 要得到一个\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Rumi. Do you know how hard it is to get a character…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕是这么小的电视剧角色有多难?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}that reappears in a drama series? Even a role like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道 但是\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yes, I do. But…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻能否成为真正的演员 就看现在了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}This is where Mima proves if she can be seen as a real actress or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.95,0:23:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我觉得 还是应该 继续让她当偶像歌手\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But we should sell Mima as a pop idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留美啊 现在跟你当偶像时相比 时代已经不同了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Really. Times are different from when Rumi Hidaka was a working pop idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.05,0:23:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如今 大众心中 已经没有偶像歌手的地位了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Nowadays, there are no places for pop idols to appeal to the masses.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻能否红下去 选择正确的发展方向很重要\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}This is the branch point that will decide if Mima lasts or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只怪我当年没一直红下去\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Well, excuse me for not surviving.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.06,0:23:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜托 留美\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Please, Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.89,0:24:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有比让未麻做演员更好的事了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}There's nothing better than having Mima be able to change into an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.60,0:24:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她来东京是为了唱歌的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}She came to Tokyo to sing…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想想\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.65,0:24:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卖唱片其实没给我们赚到多少钱\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}On record sales we make practically nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.95,0:24:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我真的希望能多给她点镜头\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But I do wish that they'd use her a little bit more…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.41,0:24:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没赚到钱真是对不起啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Sorry we're not that profitable!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.58,0:24:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早上好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.62,0:24:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}新的CHAM组合怎么样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}How's the new CHAM going?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.59,0:24:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(Double Bind)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Double Bind{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.27,0:24:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那电视剧好难看\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It's the pits!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.27,0:24:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Double Bind? 我也看了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Double Bind… yeah, I saw it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.94,0:24:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真无聊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It was so boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.70,0:24:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么日本的心理悬疑片 都是一个套路\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Why do all psycho-thrillers made in Japan turn out that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.24,0:24:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也没怎么看到未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mimarin's not in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.58,0:25:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对啊 上周她才只有4个镜头\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh yeah. How many scenes was she in last week? Four?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.58,0:25:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是3个\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.87,0:25:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谁来帮帮未麻啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Somebody save Mimarin! PLEASE!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.30,0:25:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(互联网主页 你也可以做一个)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}A HOME PAGE ON THE INTERNET: You can make one too!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.86,0:25:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天早上 我左脚先下了火车…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}This morning, when I got off the train left foot first…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.40,0:26:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗨 是未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hey, It's Mimarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.16,0:26:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早上好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.95,0:26:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早上好 未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Good morning, Mimarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.53,0:26:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}连续剧请加油啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Break a leg with that drama series!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.83,0:26:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘿 等等 未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hey, wait, Mimarin…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.20,0:26:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}变成了演员就都不友好了吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Do they get all unfriendly when they become actresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.01,0:26:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(机动车肇事逃逸)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Hit-And-Run at Shinkaido.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.51,0:26:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(土居正 18岁 重伤)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Tadashi Doi (18), in critical condition.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.57,0:26:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早上好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.49,0:26:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早上好 未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Good morning, Mima.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.78,0:27:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}干杯\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Cheers!
