Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.42,0:37:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}我再也不想演那部戏了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}I don't want to do that drama anymore!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.34,0:37:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}那个制作人完全是个变态 把我的角色搞得一团糟\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}The producer is a total pervert, and my role is really screwed up!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.47,0:37:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}在我的歌迷面前唱歌 才是我最喜欢的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Singing in front of my fans has GOT to be the best for me after all!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.69,0:38:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噢 那场戏啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh… that scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.15,0:38:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果说从没有过犹豫 那肯定是在说谎\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Of course I would be lying if I said I didn't have any hesitations…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.91,0:38:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我把它看作成为一个演员 必须跨过的障碍\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}but I looked at it as a hurdle I had to jump over as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.70,0:38:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听说收视率提高了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I heard the ratings went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.79,0:38:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一般来说 大众都是傻瓜\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}As always, the public at large are all idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.00,0:38:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的 我更愿意被看做是一个演员\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yes. I'd like to be recognized as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.96,0:38:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是"前偶像歌手"?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Not as "the ex-pop idol"?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.63,0:38:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.01,0:38:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幸好我只喜欢小丽 所以对我来说没什么关系\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I was fine coz Rei was always the one I liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.30,0:38:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我敢打赌 所有未麻的歌迷现在都在哭\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm sure all the Mimarin fans are crying right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.72,0:38:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是在CHAM的经历教会我很多 那是段难忘的经历\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But CHAM did teach me a lot. It was a great experience in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.69,0:38:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对对 就是这样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yeah, totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.90,0:38:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他们可能会大叫 "那不是真正的未麻! "\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}They're probably whining, "That's not Mimarin!"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.70,0:38:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(未麻之部屋)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Mima's Room{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.75,0:39:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的日子过得怎么样呢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What was YOUR day like?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.13,0:39:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天 我还是有点沮丧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"Today, I was still a little depressed…"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.71,0:39:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 你们的邮件 让我感觉好多了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"but receiving e-mail from all of you made me feel a little better."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.30,0:39:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}邮件?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}E-mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.80,0:39:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}6月24日 大家帮帮我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"June 24: Help me, everyone…"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.35,0:39:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每个人都在逼我去做 那完全是编剧的错\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"Everyone is forcing me to do it! It's all the screenwriter's fault!"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.65,0:39:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(救救我 救救我 救救我 救救我)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Help! Help! Help! Help! Help! Help!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.02,0:39:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这 这是假的 我没写过这样的东西\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}This… This isn't true! I'm not writing any of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.53,0:39:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}当然罗 是真正的未麻在写\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Of course! The REAL Mima is writing this!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.87,0:39:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}我能看穿你 你想再成为偶像歌手\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}I know that deep down in your heart you want to be a pop idol again.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.33,0:39:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.37,0:39:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不再\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm no longer…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.33,0:39:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}你不再什么?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}No longer what?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.46,0:39:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}哦 对 你不再是偶像歌手了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Oh, yeah, you're no longer a pop idol.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.88,0:39:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}你现在是个肮脏的女人了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}You're a filthy woman now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.01,0:39:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}没人会喜欢一个脏女人做偶像\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Nobody likes idols with tarnished reputations!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.68,0:39:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是的 不是的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}That's not true! That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.64,0:39:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mimarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.81,0:40:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}你的光芒已经消褪了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}You can't step back into that spotlight now…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.02,0:40:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}但也好 还有我呢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}But that's all right. I'M here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.61,0:40:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}从今往后 我在灯光下 你在阴影里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}From now on, I'll be in the light, and you'll be in the shadows.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.70,0:40:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在说什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What are you saying!?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.08,0:40:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你到底是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Who in the world are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.62,0:40:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}没有人会再喜欢你了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Nobody likes you anymore.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.58,0:40:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}你已经被玷污了! 脏女人!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}You're tarnished! FILTHY!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.96,0:40:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别说了!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.92,0:40:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我没有被玷污!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I am not tarnished!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.22,0:40:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别走\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.51,0:40:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别走\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.80,0:41:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Love makes your heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.22,0:41:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}If it means you're loved in the end…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.43,0:41:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}be much more aggressive…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.65,0:41:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}because you will get a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.02,0:41:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}The angel of love smiles at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.70,0:41:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有人吗?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.00,0:41:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是否看到了天使的翅膀\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Can you see the angel's white wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.59,0:41:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也许她的眼睛正注视着你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Or her eyes gazing at you…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.05,0:41:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她甜蜜的嗓音 她温柔的双手\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}her sweet voice, her gentle hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.18,0:42:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她只为你而存在\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}She is here just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.56,0:42:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她保护着你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}She is protecting you…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.94,0:42:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就在你的身边\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}from somewhere nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.03,0:42:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Got a question about…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.65,0:42:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Love makes your heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.41,0:42:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}If it means you're loved in the end…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.66,0:42:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}be much more aggressive…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.99,0:43:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}案发是凌晨1点左右\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It happened about 1 o'clock this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.45,0:43:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对了 昨晚我给你家打电话 你居然没在\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hey, I called you last night and you weren't in…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.67,0:43:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}日 被你发现了… 算了 哈哈\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"Oh shit! How did you know?" Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.71,0:43:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看到了未麻之部屋吗?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Did you see "Mima's Room"?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.80,0:43:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 那真的是她吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yeah, but is that really her?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.47,0:43:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谁知道\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}No clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.18,0:43:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}根据那个网站 未麻今天会出场表演\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}According to that page, Mimarin's gonna be on stage today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.01,0:43:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么可能\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.01,0:43:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(警方表示 死者涉谷贵雄 被利器刺中十几刀)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Police say Shibuya was stabbed umpteen times with a sharp object…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.73,0:43:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(著名编剧遭残杀 死者 涉谷贵雄 34岁)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Popular Script Writer SLAUGHTERED! The victim: Takao Shibuya (34)…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.65,0:43:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这事很可怕 但我们担心也没用\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It sure is a shocking incident, but us worrying about it won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.24,0:43:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们得把精力 放到别的事情上去\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}We have to put our minds on something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.86,0:43:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是还有炸弹信那件事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But there was that letter bomb too…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.70,0:43:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂喂 你认为涉谷的谋杀 与那事有关?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You think Mr. Shibuya's murder is connected with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.12,0:43:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我没那么说\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I didn't say that…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.08,0:43:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你电视剧看得太多了 别担心\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You watch too many TV tabloid shows. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.63,0:43:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那表情可不像个明星 笑一笑\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You won't become a star looking like that! Smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.09,0:44:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(涉谷在1990年获得新作家奖 然后…)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Shibuya won the New Writers' Prize in 1990, and then…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.39,0:44:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你.\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Serves…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.43,0:44:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.32,0:44:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了 未麻 未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What's wrong? Mima! MIMA!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.08,0:44:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻会没事吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But will Mima be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.12,0:44:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.62,0:44:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听说那个摄影师专门剥人衣服\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}That photographer specializes in getting people to strip!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.08,0:44:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那又怎么样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.79,0:44:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她已经习惯了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}She's got that part down pat!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.09,0:44:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我肯定她会在摄影师面前全脱哦\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm sure she's totally showing it off in front of the photographer!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.92,0:44:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全脱…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Like, TOTALLY!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.47,0:44:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}该你们上场了 快点\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Isn't it time you were on? Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.01,0:44:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yes'm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.65,0:44:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唔 我喜欢这个表情\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oooh… I like that expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.69,0:44:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用手拨拨头发\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Try running your fingers through your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.36,0:45:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噢噢 我喜欢这样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, I like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.69,0:45:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.58,0:45:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对 就是这样 嘴唇微微张开\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yeah, just like that. Part your lips a little…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.16,0:45:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好极了 把上衣脱下来\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Great. Now let's take the top off too…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.42,0:46:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想你早就下定了决心\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I thought you decided to go through with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.38,0:46:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都在等你呢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Everyone is waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.55,0:46:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来吧 未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Come on, Mima!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.05,0:46:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}我不是告诉过你吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}See? Didn't I tell you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.22,0:46:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}你最好还是当偶像歌手\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}You were better off as a pop idol.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.77,0:46:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 未麻 你在听吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hey Mima, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.23,0:46:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}住嘴! 你到底是谁?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Stop all this nonsense! Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.40,0:46:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}我?我是个偶像歌手\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Me? I'm a pop idol.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.57,0:46:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}大家都在等着我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Everyone's waiting for me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.70,0:46:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}所以我现在要和小丽和雪子一起演唱了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}So I'm going to sing with Rei and Yukiko again.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.57,0:46:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 不对\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.12,0:46:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是一个演员\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.83,0:46:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}别傻了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Don't be silly!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.12,0:46:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}没人希望你做那种事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}No one really wants that!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.46,0:46:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.08,0:46:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}大家希望的是…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}What everyone wants is…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.99,0:47:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢大家\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.63,0:47:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(6月27日  多谢今天的捧场)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}June 27th: Thank you for coming to the event today!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.76,0:47:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(在你们面前唱歌 是我最快乐的事)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}It really is the best feeling to sing in front of all of you!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.98,0:47:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}混蛋\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}BASTARDS!!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.82,0:47:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(脱衣女星 雾越未麻 离开偶像宝座)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Mima Kirigoe Leaving the Throne of a Pop Idol!!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.50,0:47:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.46,0:48:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.12,0:48:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你干吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.86,0:48:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(致"未麻狂人"先生: 谢谢你每天的信)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}To Mr. ME-MANIA: Thank you for your e-mail every day…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.61,0:48:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}你相信我 对吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}You believe me, right?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.03,0:48:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}那不是我 是一个冒牌货\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}That's not me. She's an impostor!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.87,0:48:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(当然 我知道未麻永远不会做那种事)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Of course. Mimarin would never do such a thing.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.37,0:48:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(我会保护你 真正的未麻)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}I will protect you, the real Mimarin.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.25,0:48:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}我相信你 未麻狂人先生\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}I trust you, Mr. ME-MANIA.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.71,0:48:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}我不会改变的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}I won't change one bit.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.17,0:48:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}我会永远和你在一起\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}I'll always be with you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.13,0:48:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}但是那个冒牌货 一直在妨碍我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}But that impostor keeps getting in my way.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.55,0:48:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}我该怎么办\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}What should I do?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.01,0:49:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}(我会搞定她)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}I'll get rid of her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.81,0:49:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}谢谢你 未麻狂人先生\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Thank you, Mr. Me-mania!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.03,0:49:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}你是我唯一的依靠\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}You're the only one I can depend on.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.21,0:49:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已经不知道我自己是谁了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I don't know anything about myself anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.63,0:49:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.63,0:49:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是什么让你能够确定\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}How do you think you know that person you were…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.63,0:49:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一秒钟前的你 和现在的你是同一个人?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}a second ago is the same person you are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.72,0:49:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}答案 记忆的连续性\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}A continuous stream of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.89,0:49:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也因为这个 我们才得以带起假面生活\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Given only that, we all create illusions within ourselves…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.39,0:49:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}假装心中没有另一个 受压制的自我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}saying that we each have only one fixed persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.94,0:49:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}医生 我很担心\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Doctor, I'm scared…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.61,0:49:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}另外一个我会做出一些 我不知道的事情\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}that my other self will do something that I don't know about…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.15,0:49:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事 幻想是不会成为现实的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It's all right. There is no way illusions can come to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.83,0:50:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卡!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}CUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.41,0:50:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻 怎么了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mima, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.25,0:50:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.04,0:50:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唉 这雨真凉\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, man! This rain sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.92,0:50:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我恐怕要感冒了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I think I'm going to catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.38,0:50:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.47,0:50:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遮起来 遮起来\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Wrap it up! Wrap it up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.19,0:50:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}风雨虽然猛烈 但你的心却充满阳光\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It's pouring really badly outside, but your heart is always, like, sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.78,0:50:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么 我们现在开始吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Well, I think we're ready today!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.99,0:50:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}"Yukiko公司"\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}and Yukiko's…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.03,0:50:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}"CHAM之家"\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"Idol Chamland"!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.50,0:50:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}田所先生\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mr. Tadokoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.41,0:50:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他们应该已经开始播音了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm sure they're on the air now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.21,0:50:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好久都没见面 你可能也想见见她们\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I thought you'd like to see them coz it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.38,0:51:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这周日下午两点 我们在茨城有个演出\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}We have a show this Sunday. It's at Ibaragi Sim City at 2pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.43,0:51:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}-好久不见 -(欢迎歌迷们来捧场)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\b0}-How have you been? {\i1}-People from all over, come see us!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.18,0:51:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}-早就想过来看看 -(我们会等着你哦)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\b0}-Just thought I'd drop by. {\i1}-We'll be waiting for you!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.64,0:51:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}CHAM之家 下周同一时间 再会\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Chamland will be back next week at the same time. Until then…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.81,0:51:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}1 2\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Two, three…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.19,0:51:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Bye Bye!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.90,0:51:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很好 各位\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Good show, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.19,0:51:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 是未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hey, it's Mima.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.74,0:51:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mima!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.23,0:51:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别走\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.23,0:51:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.99,0:52:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}我告诉过你 我是真未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}I told you! I'M the real Mima.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.90,0:52:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}下一则新闻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}In other news…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.78,0:52:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}今日 经济企划厅针对国民生活水平\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Today, the Economic Planning Agency announced a "New Citizen's Life Index"…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.24,0:52:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}发布了一项"新市民生活指数"\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}that indicates the overall Japanese standard of living and…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.96,0:52:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像好久不见了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It feels like I haven't seen you in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.79,0:52:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也很忙\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Well, I've been busy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.96,0:52:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}习惯了当演员吗?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}So, are you getting used to acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.76,0:53:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.17,0:53:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然很辛苦 但 是我自己的选择\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It's hard, but I chose to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.51,0:53:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你成熟了不少 未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You've matured quite a bit, Mima!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.72,0:53:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好在 人们似乎也很喜欢新未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But it's good that people seem to like the new Mima.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.60,0:53:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.52,0:53:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不同意吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}That doesn't look like a face that's agreeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.15,0:53:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个 未麻 有人一直在骚扰你吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You know… Mima… Has someone been harassing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.82,0:53:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一直上那个网站\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I've been visiting that home page.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.16,0:53:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然只是抱怨你形象的改变 我觉得还是过分了点\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It's a bit much, even if it's a complaint about how you changed your image…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.41,0:53:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不看会感觉好些的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It's better if you didn't look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.50,0:53:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.00,0:53:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是她可能才更像真正的未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But maybe she is more like me than myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.50,0:53:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mima?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.21,0:53:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我深埋在心底的另一个我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}My other self that I buried deep within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.38,0:53:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What if…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.51,0:53:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}另一个自我自动起作用了 该怎么办\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What if that other personality suddenly started acting on its own?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.09,0:53:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事 幻想是不会成为现实的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It's all right. There is no way illusions can come to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.85,0:53:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}停\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}CUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.77,0:53:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻 你在说什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mima! What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.23,0:54:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唉 这句台词我已经念得快吐了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I feel like I'm gonna have nightmares about this line!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.94,0:54:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.25,0:54:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.20,0:54:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 没什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Uh, nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.79,0:54:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再来一次 从头开始\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Once more, from the top…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.76,0:54:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 开始\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}All right, Take 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.64,0:54:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}下一则新闻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}In other news…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.81,0:54:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}今日 经济企划厅针对国民生活水平\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Today, the Economic Planning Agency announced a "New Citizen's Life Index"…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.27,0:54:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}发布了一项"新市民生活指数"\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}that indicates the overall Japanese standard of living and…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.77,0:54:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好久不见了 留美\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}It's been a while, Rumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.78,0:54:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啥?我昨天不是刚来过?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What? I was here yesterday, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.62,0:54:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}昨天…是真的吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yesterday? Was that real?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.62,0:54:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看起来怪怪的 未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You're weird, Mima.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.08,0:55:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻 你怎么了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mima! What's wrong with you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.29,0:55:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在流血\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.09,0:55:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这血是真的吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}This blood is real, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.01,0:55:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mima!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.56,0:55:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}(今天我去了原宿购物 我对购物最没抵抗力了)\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Today I went shopping in Harajuku. I'm a sucker for sale items.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.86,0:55:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原来 我今天去了原宿\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I guess… I went to Harajuku today…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.83,0:55:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的意思是\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.29,0:55:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个凶手只是她的幻觉\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}the murderer is an illusion she created?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.71,0:55:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.50,0:55:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她害怕一个并不存在的保安\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}She fears an imaginary security guard…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.92,0:55:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}并且把他想象成了那件 模特连环谋杀案的凶犯\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}and then doubles that figure with the serial murderer of top models.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.13,0:55:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但不存在的幻象是不会杀人的啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But illusions don't kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.76,0:55:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是 如果她把她的幻想 投射到了真实的人身上\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But… what if that illusion found someone to possess?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.02,0:55:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}投射?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Possess??
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.56,0:56:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}这么说 那些被杀的男人…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Then… all those men who got murdered?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.94,0:56:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}同时也都是 已经对她没用了的人\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Were those who were no longer of any use to her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.82,0:56:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}山城君 请快点找到她\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Find her quickly, Mr. Yamashiro.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.49,0:56:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}赶在下一个牺牲者出现前\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Before another victim falls prey.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.62,0:56:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多少钱\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.54,0:56:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你这送披萨的真够怪的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You sure are a weird pizza man.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.70,0:57:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}停下 求你了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Stop! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.26,0:57:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唔 好极了 再来 再惹火一点\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yeah, that looks good… Come on, be more daring! More passionate!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.49,0:57:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好! 第三次!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}All right! Take three!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.92,0:57:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}-喂 -未麻?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\b0}-Hello? {\i1}-Mima?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.80,0:57:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你那里没事吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Are you all right over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.34,0:57:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你还没听说村野先生的事吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You haven't heard yet… about Mr. Murano?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.47,0:58:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.68,0:58:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}警方表示村野死于多处刺伤\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Police say that Murano died of multiple stab wounds…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.98,0:58:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}村野先生他真的…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mr. Murano!? Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.85,0:58:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们这里已经乱成一团了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}We're going crazy here!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.69,0:58:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不要动 等我过去 听到了?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Anyway, stay put until I get there. All right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.99,0:58:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}据了解 此次谋杀所用的凶器 极为类似于…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}The weapon used in the latest murder is said to closely resemble…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.53,0:58:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}上周知名编剧被杀一案 的涉案凶器\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}the one used in last week's killing of a popular screenwriter.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.24,0:58:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}警方认为不排除仇杀可能\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Police are considering a personal grudge as the motive…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.12,0:58:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}并表示正努力寻找 两起案件之间可能的关联\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}and are looking into connections between the two cases.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.57,0:59:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雾越小姐 您能否谈谈您对 摄影师村野谋杀案的看法?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Miss Kirigoe! Please, can we get your opinion about the murder of Mr. Murano?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.87,0:59:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你知道些什么吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Do you know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.62,0:59:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这起事件与编剧涉谷的谋杀案 有什么关联?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Isn't there a connection with the killing of Mr. Shibuya the screenwriter?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.50,0:59:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雾越小姐 您能否谈谈…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Miss Kirigoe! There are rumors of a love triangle…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.50,0:59:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有关您 涉谷先生和村野先生之间 三角恋爱的传闻…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}between you, Mr. Shibuya, and Mr. Murano and we…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.85,0:59:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你认为她被诅咒了?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You think she's jinxed?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.06,0:59:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有一有二就有三嘛\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What happens twice happens thrice.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.31,0:59:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们赌赌下一个会是谁吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Let's take bets on who's next.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.19,0:59:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要说了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.73,0:59:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别理他们\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Don't mind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.65,0:59:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…还活着吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Am I alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.57,0:59:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也许那辆卡车撞到了我 也许这一切只是一场梦\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Maybe that truck hit me… and this is all a dream…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.12,0:59:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各就各位\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.53,0:59:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}OK. Mima!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.96,0:59:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比彩排时呼吸重一点\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Breathe harder than during rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.92,0:59:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你刚刚杀了人\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You've just killed someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.17,0:59:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.27,1:00:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}预备 开始\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}And… action!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.57,1:00:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}清醒了吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.95,1:00:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You are?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.20,1:00:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能告诉我你的名字吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Can you tell me your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.29,1:00:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我 我叫雾越未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Me? I'm Mima Kirigoe.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.63,1:00:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的 你的工作是?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Okay. And what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.63,1:00:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是一个流行乐偶像… 不 是个演员\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm a pop idol… no, an actress.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.34,1:00:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}一定很辛苦吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}That must be hard work.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.59,1:00:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}虽然很辛苦 但 是我自己的选择\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}It's hard, but it's what I chose to do.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.14,1:00:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她以为自己是个叫雾越未麻的年轻演员\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}She thinks she's a new young actress named Mima Kirigoe.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.98,1:01:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}分离性身份障碍\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Dissociative Identity Disorder.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.90,1:01:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}简单的说 多重人格\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}In other words, "multiple personality syndrome."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.16,1:01:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所有的案件都是她在 变成另一人格时犯下的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}All those crimes took place when she was some other persona.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.16,1:01:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么 阳子本来的人格到哪里去了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}So where's the persona of the original Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.50,1:01:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原始的人格高仓阳子\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Yoko Takakura, the original persona…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.13,1:01:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对她来说成了一部剧中的人物\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}is nothing more than a character in a drama for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.17,1:01:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她本人曾是个普通的女孩 曾在脱衣舞夜总会里被强奸\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Being a "normal" girl… how she was raped in a strip club…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.76,1:01:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她把这些事 全都当作是剧中的情节\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Everything happened as part of her drama series.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.35,1:01:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以此来得到解脱\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}By doing so, she salvaged her heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.81,1:01:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的 我是一个演员\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}That's right. I'm an actress.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.65,1:01:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卡!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Cut!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.11,1:01:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}能告诉我你的名字吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Can you tell me your name?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.32,1:01:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}我 我叫高仓莉香\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Me? I'm Rika Takakura.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.28,1:01:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原始的人格 高仓阳子 已经不存在了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}The original persona, Yoko Takakura, no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.16,1:01:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她杀死当模特的姐姐后 自己变成姐姐 以此来得到解脱\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}By killing, and later becoming, her sister the top-model, she salvaged her heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.30,1:02:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的 我是一个模特\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}That's right. I'm a model.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.67,1:02:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 成了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}All right! That's the take!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.52,1:02:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了! 未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}We did it, Mima!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.40,1:02:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻 干得好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mima… Good work!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.94,1:02:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真的很努力\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I can tell you tried so hard!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.86,1:02:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留美…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Rumi…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.24,1:02:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我宣布 Double Bind 至此全部拍摄完毕\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}As of this moment, Double Bind is in the can!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.83,1:02:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家幸苦了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Everyone, great job!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.26,1:02:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻真的太棒了 你说是不是啊 导演\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You were fantastic, Mima! What do you think, Director?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.31,1:02:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她确实很出色\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}She really was excellent.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.60,1:02:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢你们\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.27,1:02:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么 庆功宴上见\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}See you at the wrap-up party.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.94,1:03:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还请多指教\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}We'll be talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.11,1:03:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么 我们也走吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Then… shall we go as well?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.94,1:03:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻 去换衣服\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mima, go get changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.79,1:03:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瞳子医生…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Dr. Touko…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.63,1:03:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈 我已经不是瞳子了 你忘了?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Hey now! I'm not Touko anymore! Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.92,1:03:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}"幻想是不会成为现实的"\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}"There is no way illusions can come to life."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.39,1:03:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}赶快从梦中醒来吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You should stop dreaming soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.44,1:03:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}惠利小姐?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Eri?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.32,1:03:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻怎么去了这么久\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What's taking Mima so long?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.66,1:03:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我先回事务所 你送未麻回家吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm going back to the office. Take Mima home, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.87,1:04:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}田所先生 你刚才提到 未麻的下一份工作是?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mr. Tadokoro. You were saying something about Mima's next job?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.42,1:04:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噢 挺不错的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, it's great!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.50,1:04:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是一部电影的女主角\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}A starring role in a video movie.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.21,1:04:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这次要下更大的决心才行 不过这也是没办法的嘛\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}There are a few sketchy scenes… but what can you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.55,1:04:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救救我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Somebody help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.43,1:04:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有人会听到的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Like anyone can hear YOUR voice right now!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.44,1:04:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是谁?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.57,1:04:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么要这样?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Why are you doing this!?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.94,1:04:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是在保护我的宝贝未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm protecting my dear Mimarin!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.78,1:04:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…我就是未麻啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But-But I'm Mima!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.03,1:04:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不不不不不\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}No, no, no, no, NO!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.08,1:04:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你都不知道我就是"未麻狂人"\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You didn't know I was Me-mania!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.87,1:04:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你只是装成未麻的样子\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You're just PRETENDING to be Mimarin!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.37,1:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}住手 不要 不要\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}STOP!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.50,1:04:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 不要\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}NO! STOP!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.51,1:04:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你用这张小嘴 勾引了那位编剧和摄影师\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Did you fool that screenwriter and that photographer with this little mouth?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.05,1:04:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你玷污了未麻的名字!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You tarnished Mimarin's name!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.14,1:05:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道…是你?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Can it be… that you…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.89,1:05:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真正的未麻每天都发邮件给我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}The real Mimarin e-mails me every day!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.60,1:05:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她说你一直都在妨碍她\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}And she says that you keep getting in her way!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.61,1:05:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是你杀了他们?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You killed them!?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.57,1:05:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也就快死了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}And you'll die soon, too!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.75,1:05:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}坏女人\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Bad girl!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.13,1:05:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要按照剧本演才对\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You have to follow the script!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.09,1:05:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在 开始\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}And now… TAKE 2!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.52,1:07:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 很不错\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}All right! Looks good!!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.03,1:07:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是最棒的 未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You're the best, Mima!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.67,1:07:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Mima!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.55,1:07:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎么成这样了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What's wrong? You're in shambles!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.76,1:07:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我到处找你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I was looking all over for you!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.68,1:07:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留美…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Rumi…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.56,1:07:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到底发生了什么事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.15,1:08:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可能\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}This can't be!!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.20,1:08:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你确定不是做梦?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Are you sure you weren't dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.92,1:08:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你没事吧?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.21,1:08:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我带你回 未麻之部屋\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm taking you back… to Mima's room.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.49,1:08:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留美 你在吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Rumi, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.74,1:08:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.16,1:08:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噢 没事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, nothing…
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.25,1:08:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对了 得给田所先生打个电话\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, that's right, I have to call Mr. Tadokoro.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.85,1:09:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 这不是我的房间\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}No… This isn't my room…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.23,1:09:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\b1\fs16}当然不是 因为这里是未麻之部屋嘛\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\i1\b0}Of course not! This is Mima's room!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.15,1:10:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You're!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.57,1:10:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看 我的新衣服\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Look! It's the new costume!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.95,1:10:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天演出要穿\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'm wearing it at tomorrow's show!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.08,1:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好看吧?很合身呢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Isn't it great? It's perfect on me!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.96,1:10:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留美?为什么?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Rumi? Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.88,1:10:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留美?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.71,1:10:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留美…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Rumi…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.38,1:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留美已经回家了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh! Rumi went home.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.76,1:10:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她说最近工作太累 要补一补觉\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}She said she's been busy lately and was deprived of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.22,1:10:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请别说这些奇怪的话了!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Don't say weird stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.76,1:10:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是个玩笑 对不对 留美\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}This is a joke, isn't it, Rumi!?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.39,1:10:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果你发现自己心跳不已\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Love makes your heart race.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.73,1:10:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那意味着爱已降临\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}If it means you're loved in the end…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.73,1:10:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎样?唱得好吧?\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}What do you think? Perfect, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.77,1:10:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偶像歌手还是得唱歌才行\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}A pop idol HAS to sing, after all!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.74,1:10:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.20,1:10:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你却总是在妨碍我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You just had to keep getting in my way.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.41,1:10:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留美她也很生气哦\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Rumi was totally furious, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.74,1:10:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}求求你 别这样了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Please… stop all of this!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.58,1:10:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但偶像总有歌迷保护\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But a pop idol is always protected by her fans!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.92,1:11:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管未麻向他们要求什么 他们都会答应!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}They listen to any favor I, Mima, ask them!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.17,1:11:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然未麻狂人先生没有做到\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Although Mr. Me-mania failed a wee bit…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.84,1:11:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未麻狂人 你是怎么知道他的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Me-mania? How do you know him!?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.22,1:11:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是他们说 "种瓜得瓜 种豆得豆" 对你来说 更是如此\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But, oh, well…" you reap what you sow," especially about YOU.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.12,1:12:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救命 来人救救我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Help! Somebody help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.55,1:13:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留美 是你吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Please! Rumi, it's you, isn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.80,1:13:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快醒醒啊!\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}PLEASE WAKE UP!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.30,1:13:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}该醒醒的是你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}YOU'RE the one who needs to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.69,1:13:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救命 救救我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Help, help, somebody!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.07,1:13:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救命 快救救我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Help! SOMEBODY HELP ME!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.24,1:13:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救救我 快来人救救我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}SOMEBODY! SOMEBODY HELP ME!!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.08,1:13:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救命 快救救我啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}HELP! SOMEBODY HELP ME!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.78,1:14:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}结束吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Let's end all of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.86,1:14:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们不需要有两个未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}We don't need two Mimas!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.20,1:14:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才是未麻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I AM MIMA!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.95,1:14:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别开玩笑了 未麻是偶像歌手\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}That's funny! Mima is a pop idol!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.12,1:14:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你只是个肮脏的假货\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You're just a dirty old impostor!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.54,1:14:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才不管 我就是我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}LIKE I CARE! I AM WHO I AM!!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.70,1:15:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噢 天啊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.66,1:15:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快叫警察 不 叫救护车\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Get the police! No, call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.08,1:15:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I know!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.72,1:16:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢你每次送的花\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Thank you for the flowers you always bring.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.39,1:16:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我会把它们摆在房间里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I'll put them in my room.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.23,1:16:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很美 很漂亮\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}They're pretty. Very pretty…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.24,1:17:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你来了啊 最近应该很忙吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I didn't know you were visiting. You must be very busy lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.62,1:17:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 哪里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.83,1:17:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她偶尔会变回留美 可是…\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}Once in a while, she returns to her Rumi persona, but…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.87,1:17:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道我不会再见到她了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}I know I'll never see HER ever again.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.67,1:17:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 也多亏了她 我才能成为今天的自己\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}But, thanks to her, I am who I am today.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.47,1:17:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}骗人的吧 雾越未麻怎么会来这地方\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12}You're lying! There's no way Mima Kirigoe would be HERE of all places!
