Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.35,0:47:08.35,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文仿宋\an2\b1\pos(192,272)\fs15}♪ 因为这孤独只属于我自己\N{\fn华文隶书\fs12\b0}♪ I have finally found a luxurious loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.80,1:18:08.85,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ Each time I pass this station on the train…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.93,1:18:16.31,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ my heart fills with nostalgia.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.40,1:18:24.40,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ The days when I ran around town, hiding all of my feelings…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.86,1:18:30.99,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ in my school uniform.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.04,1:18:37.71,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ Take me to the first time I was in love…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.79,1:18:45.79,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ those four seasons when I was frantic yet doubtful.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.88,1:18:52.56,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ Remember all those times when just being near each other…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.64,1:19:00.64,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ kept our love for each other growing?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.33,1:19:23.25,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ I cut my hair after graduation.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.34,1:19:30.84,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ I wonder if you are still the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.89,1:19:38.89,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ Are you still pursuing that dream that you kept telling me about…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.27,1:19:45.36,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.44,1:19:52.24,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ Take me to when my tears overflowed…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.28,1:20:00.28,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ to those four seasons that I felt from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.37,1:20:07.05,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ Remember how in the sunsets after school…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.13,1:20:15.13,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ we just wanted time to spend alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.24,1:20:36.83,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ Even in this new season, I can't shake…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.91,1:20:44.91,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ the habit of bluffing when I am sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.09,1:20:51.72,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ I'm sure that you knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.80,1:20:59.80,LRC,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fn华文隶书}♪ I still remember your eyes when you looked at me silently.
